#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_401_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_401_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The Jueyun Peaks spear into the sea of clouds, linked by iron chains and "
"cloud bridges over perilous mountain paths. Only those who can truly steady "
"their sword intent may climb to the highest reaches. Midway up stand sword-"
"testing platforms, sword-washing pools, and sheer cliffs carved with "
"countless blade marks; higher still, the wind grows sharper and lightning "
"sometimes flashes past the precipices. The entire mountain gate feels like "
"an ancient sword drawn but never sheathed, austere, towering, and edged with"
" cold menace."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_401_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_401_NAME"
msgstr "Jueyun Peak"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_402_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_402_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Myriad Beasts Cavern lies hidden in the depths of the mountain ranges, its "
"outer layers sealed by miasma and tangled vines that form a natural barrier."
" Only by going deeper does one reach the descending beast domains within. "
"Stone bridges, iron gates, and beast-taming platforms divide the layers, "
"while low roars and clashing chains echo without end through air thick with "
"lingering demon qi. Bones and claw marks scatter across the ground. This is "
"less a normal mountain gate than a living nest-city of colossal beasts, and "
"every lower level feels more oppressive than the last."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_402_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_402_NAME"
msgstr "Ten Thousand Beasts Cave"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_403_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_403_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Jinghaiya hangs above a sheer sea cliff, where halls, corridors, and tide-"
"viewing terraces of frost spirit jade lie half-veiled in ocean mist. From "
"afar, the entire mountain gate seems to float inside moonlight and surf. At "
"the cliffside, the jade wall reflects sea and stars, and as the tides rise "
"and fall, watery gleams ripple across walls and floors until paths seem half"
" real and half illusion. It is so quiet here that only waves, wind, and the "
"occasional bell brushing an eave remind visitors they have not yet stepped "
"outside the mortal world."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_403_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_403_NAME"
msgstr "Silent Sea Cliff"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_404_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_404_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The Dead Sea is made of black islands and shadowed bays linked by narrow "
"plank bridges, ruined ferry markers, and ghostfire lighthouses, so that from"
" afar it resembles a city of specters drifting atop ink-dark waters. The sea"
" surges without wind, and each rising wave carries a shriek like distant "
"weeping. The halls and stone steps on the islands are stained gray-white and"
" sickly green by clammy mist. At night, moonlight matters less than the soul"
" lamps flickering through the fog, turning the whole region into something "
"like the underworld seen in a dream."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_404_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_404_NAME"
msgstr "Dead Silence Sea"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_405_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_405_DESC"
msgstr ""
"At first glance Qianji Valley looks like an ordinary mountain valley, with "
"blue stone roads, elegant eaves, and carefully arranged courtyards and "
"flowers. Only on approach does one realize that bridges can turn, walls can "
"open and close, and even the height of the stairs conceals trigger "
"mechanisms. Watchtowers and suspended bridges stand above, while secret "
"tunnels, workshops, and sealed chambers lie below. Now and then one hears "
"gear teeth bite, metal hum softly, or puppet footsteps approach from "
"nowhere. The most terrifying thing here is not a single trap, but that the "
"whole valley is itself a giant machine."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_405_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_405_NAME"
msgstr "Thousand Mechanisms Valley"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_406_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_406_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The Gilded Den lies in a private heaven hidden behind a prosperous market "
"city. At the entrance are seas of lanterns, drifting incense, curved "
"bridges, and layered pavilions over the water. The deeper one goes, the more"
" the clamor fades and the more lingering the sounds of water and music "
"become. Outer terraces glitter with gold and jade and overflow with guests, "
"while deeper within lie quiet rooms, hot springs, and dream pools hidden "
"behind gauze, flower walls, and mist. Everything here is beautiful and "
"luxurious, yet it is impossible to tell whether one has come to feast, to "
"dream, or to step into a subtler kind of cultivation."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_406_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_406_NAME"
msgstr "Gold-Squandering Cave"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_407_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_407_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Pudu Island hangs alone in the center of the Storm Sea. Outside its shores, "
"colossal waves rise and lightning churns, yet within, bells and Buddhist "
"light press the island into an almost frozen calm. The Vajra Pagoda stands "
"at the center, ringed by temple halls, stone steps, sea-cliff austerity "
"platforms, and a harbor facing the water. Golden bells at the top ring with "
"the sea wind and seem to smooth the storm little by little. When morning "
"mist lifts, gold light falls over black reefs and pale halls, and the island"
" looks like a sacred seal lifted from an angry sea."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_407_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_407_NAME"
msgstr "Pudu Island"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_408_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_408_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Shadow Marsh never sees true daylight. Poison fog, foul water, and tangled "
"ancient trees seal the whole region shut, and intruders are often watched by"
" unseen eyes before they ever glimpse the mountain gate. The real stronghold"
" is not concentrated on the surface: hidden towers and rope bridges lie in "
"the canopy, while tunnels, cells, and miasma-covered entrances spread "
"beneath the bog. There is almost no open line of sight here, only cold lamps"
" flickering through drifting mist and black waters ready to swallow the "
"sound of footsteps at any moment."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_408_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_408_NAME"
msgstr "Shadow Swamp"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_409_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_409_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Duobao Floating Isles are not one island but a chain of differently sized "
"sky-islands linked by giant chains, cloud bridges, and cloudship routes into"
" an immortal city suspended in the heavens. The outer ring is filled with "
"busy docks and cargo yards, the middle levels with trade streets, auction "
"houses, and markets, and the heights with forging towers that vent furnace "
"fire day and night. After dark, lamps run along chains and skyways into the "
"clouds, making the whole region look like a golden mercantile web spread "
"across the sky, forever noisy and forever in motion."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_409_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_409_NAME"
msgstr "Myriad Treasures Floating Island"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_410_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_410_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Echo Valley narrows between towering cliffs, naturally forming countless "
"resonance holes and sound fissures. Even a single plucked note can whirl "
"through the valley for a long time without fading. Pavilions, waterside "
"terraces, qin towers, and corridors follow the mountain contours while "
"streams run straight through the buildings. On the surface it is as graceful"
" as an immortal retreat, yet careful listening reveals that wind past the "
"eaves and drops striking water seem rearranged by an unseen hand. The valley"
" is often most dangerous not when music fills it, but when everything "
"suddenly falls silent."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_410_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_410_NAME"
msgstr "Echo Valley"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_411_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_411_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Mizhongtian appears to be only a solitary peak, but once one enters the "
"mountain gate, terraces, steps, bridges, and roads all prove to be embedded "
"inside layers of folded space. The same road may look completely different "
"when seen from before and after. On the slopes stand plazas engraved with "
"array patterns, corridors suspended in midair, and halls that fade in and "
"out of sight, while lines of light sometimes flow across the ground as if "
"the mountain itself were slowly thinking. There is no stable sense of "
"direction here; every step feels like entering another world."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_411_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_411_NAME"
msgstr "Maze Heaven"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_412_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_412_DESC"
msgstr ""
"Aurora Heaven lies in the depths of the far northern eternal night. Beyond "
"it stretch silent ice plains, yet this palace city alone is bathed year-"
"round in moving aurora bright as day. Lofty ice walls, black-iron gates, "
"frozen bridges, and training grounds gleam beneath the shifting light, while"
" deep within the city the sacred flame altar casts a steady warmth-red glow "
"through the cold. Its beauty is not merely grandeur, but the ordered "
"coexistence of ice and fire, stillness and radiance, as if the whole city "
"were a flame enduring inside the deepest winter."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_412_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_412_NAME"
msgstr "Aurora Heaven Realm"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_413_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_413_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The Forest of Sages stands where central spirit veins converge, filled with "
"towering ancient trees and scattered stone steles. Lecture halls, libraries,"
" and waterside courtyards are tucked among the shade, and anyone walking "
"there must often pass along leaf-strewn paths and corridors carved with "
"classical inscriptions. By day, the sound of reading travels far with the "
"forest wind; by night, the steles emit a faint glow under the moon, leaving "
"trees and eaves wrapped in quiet dignity. The place feels less like a closed"
" sect and more like a living academy still growing with time."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_413_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_413_NAME"
msgstr "Sage Forest"

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_414_DESC
msgid "SECT_REGION_414_DESC"
msgstr ""
"The mountain above the Shura Blood Pool is dark red through and through, "
"with blood-colored mist and heat rising constantly from its cracks. Deep "
"inside the mountain, immense underground blood pools and layered sacrificial"
" halls have been hollowed out of the earth. Iron chain bridges span blood "
"rivers, and stone stairs descend toward battle platforms, bone caves, and "
"altars lit by scarlet light. The deeper one goes, the heavier the scent of "
"rust, medicine, and damp blood becomes. The entire stronghold feels like a "
"monstrous beast breathing slowly beneath the ground."

#. sect_region.csv: SECT_REGION_414_NAME
msgid "SECT_REGION_414_NAME"
msgstr "Asura Blood Pool"
